translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 殺到し、斧で頭を叩き割ろうとする魔物兵に対し、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Against the demon soldiers who surged forward trying to smash his head with axes,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ポロンは素早く懐に飛び込み、胴体に拳を叩き込む。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Poron swiftly leapt into their range and punched them in the torso.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 二人目の魔物兵の顎を突き砕く。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: shattered the jaw of the second demon soldier.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一人で我々を食い止める気か！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Does he intend to hold us back all by himself!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「わ……来た来た。そろそろだ、っと！」
不意に、ポロンは背中を向けて逃げ出した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Suddenly, Poron turned his back and fled.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今さら逃がすと思うか！　殺せ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You really think we'll let him escape now? Kill him!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あいつは昔、少々特殊な冒険をしてな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "He went on a rather unusual adventure in the past."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 追いついたピッテンは、
走りながら器用に頭を抱えた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: skillfully held his head while running.
"Well... to cut out a lot of details,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: どうもずっと、冒険の最中に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he apparently was constantly chased from behind during his adventures.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 背後から追いかけられ続けていたらしい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He was continually pursued from behind."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「そこは俺にもよく分からん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I don't really know that part either.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 精神的なものかもしれん」
「……が、今でも、ギリギリで追いかけられながら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "...But even now, he seems to have gotten used to running while barely being chased.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 走るのが性に合うようになったらしい」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems it's become his nature to do so."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「起きる事象はよく似ているが……
ま、元々人助けを苦にしない性格だからな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Well, he's originally the type who doesn't mind helping others."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ほっといていいのかい？　王様だろ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Is it okay to just leave him like that? Isn't he the king?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「良くわからん兄弟だな、お前ら……」
人間の足で走れるって、いいなぁ……！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Running on human legs is truly wonderful...!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ポロンはしんがりを務めながら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While acting as rear guard, Poron

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 風のように疾走していった。
「すみません、荷物持って頂いて……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Sorry for making you carry the luggage..."
"No, it was on the way anyway.
